thread.title_full: Totally Wicked E-liquid USA inc. reviewed by Roger HInman

author: Roger HInman
title: Roger HInman
text:
This is an excellent company. Fast shipping, great products and a excellent over all experience.
I have on rare occasion received and item that did not preform correctly and customer service has been more that helpful, they have replaced the items free of charge in an efficient and professional manner.
I highly recommend Totally Wicked E-Liquid. You will not be disappointed.
